➜百公里最低仅1.5L！插混与油车同价，试驾吉利博瑞ePro
http://www.sohu.com/a/413486394_99994080	35279
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200819/323655b6d6704c62aa5768c50dd9485f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/98ab60e44d024f1d9a7a32098581fb91.png" max-width="600" /></p>
